headline: Motorola Solutions (MSI) Margin Gains Reinforce Bullish Narrative Despite Slower Growth Versus Market
summary: Motorola Solutions (MSI) posted standout earnings growth of 35.6%, significantly outpacing its 5-year average of 15.1% per year. Profit margins climbed to 18.7% from last year's 14.7%, and while earnings and revenue are forecast to rise at 9.09% and 6.8% per year respectively, both figures trail the broader US market averages.
